---
title: Quick Seared Chicken & Cauli-Potato Mash with Creamy Celery Slaw
description: Say goodbye to plain old taters in your mash because cauliflower's here and it's lending incredible flavour and
texture to a once familiar side that's now a delightful companion to delicious, spiced chicken! Sorry potatoes...
been there, done that.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
